From New York City Powerviolence legends Black Army Jacket comes comes an updated 59 song discography that collects unreleased 7"s, the 1996 demo, "The Path of Two Swords as One" 7", various compilation tracks, and split releases with Agathocles, Corrupted, Hemlock, Noothgrush, and Spazz.

2xLP on Brainscan Records and State of Mind Recordings
Digital on Pax Aeternum
